description:
Shane Erickson is back once again. This time he's here to break his even record of
2-2. He's shown that he's got skill on the mat; his losses have all been close matches while his victories have been landslides. This week he's up against Jake Woods, a spunky newcomer who isn't afraid to give it his all for the prize of Shane's ass. Can Jake prove that he's an NK contender by taking down Shane, or will he merely become another notch on Shane's belt?
title: Shane Erickson vs Jake Woods
